MODIFICATIONS IN THIS FORK:

This fork contains the following custom extensions and modifications:

1. ava_v1 Agent Integration
   - LangChain/LangGraph port of AVA hotel booking agent
   - CallContext-based dynamic prompt system (5-level priority)
   - Redis-backed caching for hotel searches and booking idempotency
   - Integration with external Pinecone service for hotel data

2. JWT Authentication System
   - Sub-1ms latency JWT authentication with LRU caching
   - HS256 symmetric signing
   - Multi-tenant user scoping via JWT claims
   - Issuer-based scope mapping for microservice integration
   - Token generation scripts and comprehensive documentation

3. Redis Integration
   - Redis caching layer for ava_v1 agent operations
   - Configurable TTL for search results (30 days) and bookings (10 minutes)
   - Docker Compose service configuration

4. Railway Deployment Support
   - Staging environment configuration for Railway.app
   - GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline for development branch
   - Railway-specific environment variable examples
   - Comprehensive deployment documentation

5. Documentation Enhancements
   - JWT authentication guide with security considerations
   - Railway deployment guide with step-by-step instructions
   - AVA prompt architecture documentation
   - Context stack management guide
   - State endpoint API documentation
   - Conversation transcript API documentation
   - Enhanced developer guides and migration cheatsheets

6. Database Schema Changes
   - Additional Alembic migrations for fork-specific features
   - Schema changes to support JWT auth and multi-tenancy

